# Component Patterns

## Server-First Architecture

- **Default to Server Components** - No directive needed
- **Add `"use client"` only at leaf components** that need:
  - React hooks (useState, useEffect, etc.)
  - Browser APIs (window, document, localStorage)
  - Event handlers (onClick, onChange, etc.)
  - Third-party client libraries

## Type Location

**NEVER define types inline in components.** All types go in `/types`:

```typescript
// ❌ Bad - inline type
interface CardProps {
  title: string;
}

// ✅ Good - import from types/
import type { CardProps } from "types/props";
```

## Styling

Use semantic design system classes:

```typescript
// ❌ Bad
<p className="text-gray-600">Text</p>

// ✅ Good
<p className="text-foreground/80">Text</p>
```

## Links

Always use Link from i18n routing:

```typescript
// ❌ Bad
import Link from "next/link";

// ✅ Good
import { Link } from "@i18n/routing";
```

